## Reviewer checklist

For a new frontend PR:

- [ ] Rendering choice documented (per-route if mixed)
- [ ] Bundle delta within budget (CI report attached)
- [ ] State changes use the right bucket (local / server / global)
- [ ] `axe-core` passes; keyboard reachable; contrast checked
- [ ] No new Core Web Vitals regression (lab + RUM if available)
- [ ] Tests at the right layer (unit for logic, component for UI, E2E for critical flows)
- [ ] No new dependency unless justified; lockfile up to date
- [ ] No secrets in client code; only `PUBLIC_*` / `VITE_*` / `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` env vars
- [ ] CSP unchanged or tightened, never loosened

